channel.description: Hi everybody. I was a fool and made a terrible mistake. I wanted to improve surface tension skybox and changed it's color a bit. Accidentaly I forgot to make a backup and I need only one file which I can't recover. So I would be really glad and happy if somebody could upload one file on mediafire or other upload service. I'm talking about " sky_st_day_01_hdr_lf ". You can find here : BMS/materials/skybox and then the file I asked you to upload. It's one VTF file so I hope it's not big deal. Thanks !
